episodes.title: Tsuut’ina police update Nathan Chasing Horse charges
episodes.description: Tsuut’ina police say it will be up to the Attorney General as to whether or not an actor accused of sex crimes will be extradited to Canada to go before a judge.

episodes.title: 'Dances with Wolves' actor faces more charges in Alberta
episodes.description: Police in Alberta have issued warrants for Nathan Chasing Horse, a former actor in the movie “Dances With Wolves,” for nine charges, including sexual exploitation, sexual assault and sexual interference of a person under 16 years old.

episodes.title: Exploring the secret world of Plymouth Brethren Christian Church
episodes.description: All week and in an upcoming documentary, CityNews is looking at a exclusive Christian Sect. The Plymouth Brethren Christian Church. So what is this religion and where did it start? Pat Taney reports.

episodes.title: Leaving the Jehovah's Witnesses
episodes.description: A rare and revealing look inside the Jehovah's Witnesses from three people who have left the religion
